SocialMediaApp using mongodb and WPF. First task from NoSql subject in Ivan Franko National University of Lviv.

App is implemented  with subscribers and followers logic. (friends)

Insert data ( read data.txt).

Dall {
  crud logic
  entities
  }

ConnectionRepository {
  to get mongodb client
  }
  
Bll {
    business logic
    helper{
      Convertor (Castom automapper)
      Hash (Md5)
    }
  }

Models {
  Models(DTO)
  }
  
